# Input

```scss
.box{
content:"foo #{$bar} baz";
path:'#{$name}.scss';
suffix:"icon-#{$name}";
only:"#{$value}";
adjacent:"#{$scheme}#{$host}";
escaped:"foo \#{$bar} baz";
background:url(#{$raw});
asset:url("https://#{$host}/#{$path}");
}

```


# Formatted

```scss
.box {
	content: "foo #{$bar} baz";
	path: "#{$name}.scss";
	suffix: "icon-#{$name}";
	only: "#{$value}";
	adjacent: "#{$scheme}#{$host}";
	escaped: "foo \#{$bar} baz";
	background: url(#{$raw});
	asset: url("https://#{$host}/#{$path}");
}

```
